00:54:37,369 --> 00:54:39,830
Sekarang kami hidup bersama manusia biasa.

749
00:54:39,913 --> 00:54:44,543
Tapi kami sering tidur
di langit-langit rumah.

750
00:54:44,626 --> 00:54:45,836
Seperti kelelawar.

751
