756
00:55:04,855 --> 00:55:08,192
Kami juga suka benda berkilau.

757
00:55:08,692 --> 00:55:13,030
Kristal, kaca, dan emas.

758
00:55:13,113 --> 00:55:16,992
"Suka benda berkilau."

759
00:55:18,077 --> 00:55:19,370
